First, asume that you already have Oracle Virtual Box:

Download the server ISO for free from https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/evalcenter/download-windows-server-2022

And download Window 11 client ISO from https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/software-download/windows11

Create Natnetwork in the Orcale virtual box, right after install, choose that as network interface
Disable DHCP because the server going to do that for us.


