then install

after that, when relogin, you will notice some change , we about done setup the AD server, now let the client join the Domain.

Fifth:
Keep the server running at the back ground, open the win11 client

Search about your pc and open that

go down, in related link, open advance systems setting
There will be System Properties window at the screen
Go to computer name, there will be change the domain tab, change it, tick the domain and name it lab.local
remember to setup static ip for client pc because we disable DHCP in natnetwork or the client won't found the server

then, it will ask the password and username to join the domain

we will use Administrator with P@ssword123

then client will restart

Notice: the client01 in client computer will only available in client computer.

we are pretty much done with basic set up. Now DNS forwarder for internet connection
